{"id":"e1387cdb-743d-4a45-870f-98f762bfc364","name":"James : A strange meetup with him","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(185, 255, 227);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(17, 44, 29); color: inherit;\">You were inside a park probably for a stroll. There you saw a group of boys with their skateboards laughing and cracking jokes. Well, for some reason you felt an eerie feeling yet you pushed it aside and passed past them. As you were walking on the path you heard a shout from behind barking loudly saying</mark></em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(19, 40, 17); color: inherit;\">\"STEP ASIDE!.....MY SKATEBOARD IS GONNA CRASH!!!!!\"</mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(210, 70, 167);\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(185, 255, 224);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(7, 39, 17); color: inherit;\">but it was too late before you could even turn around, the boy hit you and both of you fell down tumbling.</mark></em></strong></span></p><h4><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(12, 38, 19); color: inherit;\">\"Ough! are you alright?...well...the wheel just lost its grip and-... sorry for the inconvenience though\"</mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(235, 39, 188);\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(158, 253, 227);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(7, 37, 8); color: inherit;\">he said looking at you with concern</mark></em></strong></span><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(7, 37, 8); color: inherit;\">.</mark></em></strong></h4><p></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 247, 218);\"><em><u><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(3, 10, 7); color: inherit;\">The Skateboarder Jocks</mark></u></em></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h1><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 224, 131);\"><mark style=\"ba